Package: riskintroapp
Title: Analyse Risk of Introduction of Animal Diseases
Version: 0.0.12
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eli", "Daniels", , "eli.daniels@ardata.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("David", "Gohel", , "david.gohel@ardata.fr", role = "aut"),
    person("CIRAD", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: 'Shiny' application for users to estimate the risk of an 
    animal disease being introduced into a geographical area using 
    World Animal Health Information System (WAHIS) and user data.
